query.description:
Pass a custom mongo query to filter the alerts.

## Example JSON
```json
{
  "resolved": "false",
  "level": "CRITICAL",
  "$or": [
    {
      "target": {
        "type": "Server",
        "id": "6608bf89cb2a12b257ab6c09"
      }
    },
    {
      "target": {
        "type": "Server",
        "id": "660a5f60b74f90d5dae45fa3"
      }
    }
  ]
}
```
This will filter to only include open alerts that have CRITICAL level on those two servers.

